{"tid":1267864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢夢見 撐警大會rundown....","createTime":"2019-06-30T06:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T06:19:14.000Z","uid":3067,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da64fd33fc77d90399e057408ef2abf7494ed833","tid":1267864,"uid":3067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:05:51.000Z","msg":"岩岩發夢夢見 <br />\n<br />\n1500-1515<br />\n主持：鄧德成<br />\n集會正式開始，何議員上台發言，公佈集會目的，歡迎出席嘉賓及市民<br />\n<br />\n1515-1525<br />\n高志森第一位發言<br />\n<br />\n1525-1540<br />\n大電視播放短片（短片1）<br />\n<br />\n1540-1510<br />\n退休警察 陸海豪發言<br />\n<br />\n1510-1520<br />\n退休警察 畢Sir上台為現役警察兒子打氣<br />\n<br />\n1520-1535<br />\n大電視受傷警察片段（短片2）<br />\n<br />\n1535-1545<br />\n受傷警察家屬或朋友代表發言<br />\n<br />\n1545-1600<br />\n鼓手敲大鼓2個打氣，激勵士氣，喊口號<br />\n口號：撐警隊、保治安、撥亂反正<br />\n<br />\n1600-1615<br />\n何議員上台解說逃犯條例<br />\n<br />\n1615-1625<br />\n葉劉<br />\n<br />\n1625-1635<br />\n陳健波<br />\n<br />\n1635-1645<br />\n何俊賢<br />\n<br />\n1645-1700<br />\n大電視播放撐警歌曲（留意版權/ 二次創次）<br />\n（已經錄音）<br />\n<br />\n1700-1710<br />\n阿叻<br />\n<br />\n1710-1720<br />\n鄧慧詩<br />\n<br />\n1720-1740<br />\n何議員再次上台總結<br />\n<br />\n1740-1755<br />\n邀請各位嘉賓上台大合照，一起宣言支持警隊維護治安。<br />\n<br />\n1755<br />\n大會宣佈集會完成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n1755-1825<br />\n魚貫離場，由在場保安沿途監控<br />\n<br />\n1830-<br />\n義工清潔場地<br />\n承包商拆台離場"},{"pid":"5b297e97ad4306e4d7ab7f987c42b1fa6ff72431","tid":1267864,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"87e21c1a15c5cb5c8af993efd32bab71c22aab6e","tid":1267864,"uid":29703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T06:11:07.000Z","msg":"消失的到小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210310f8f945728a587723523437a3e3af5e8457","tid":1267864,"uid":29703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87e21c1a15c5cb5c8af993efd32bab71c2